<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 12:44:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>比特币“鲸鱼”抛售削弱了新的机构需求</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/bitcoin-buying-fails-to-offset-a-wave-of-selling-by-big-holders</link><description>尽管机构购买有所增加，但比特币需求仍然面临压力，这表明更广泛的市场仍在抛售该代币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iuZpxHDg1q1s/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 22:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/bitcoin-buying-fails-to-offset-a-wave-of-selling-by-big-holders</guid></item><item><title>特朗普暗示对伊朗实施更严厉打击，比特币随股市暴跌</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/bitcoin-tumbles-with-stocks-as-trump-signals-harder-iran-strikes</link><description>在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示未来几周将对伊朗实施更严厉的打击后，比特币暴跌，削弱了对战争迅速结束的乐观情绪，并导致风险资产走低。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iX.3JMnxMaug/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 04:10:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/bitcoin-tumbles-with-stocks-as-trump-signals-harder-iran-strikes</guid></item><item><title>CFTC 解决了针对前 FTX 工程主管 Singh 的案件</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/cftc-resolves-fraud-case-against-ex-ftx-engineering-chief-singh</link><description>根据与美国衍生品监管机构就其在倒闭的加密货币交易所中所扮演角色达成的和解协议，前 FTX 工程主管尼沙德·辛格 (Nishad Singh) 必须返还 370 万美元的非法利润。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioAh7.q6.eug/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 19:36:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/cftc-resolves-fraud-case-against-ex-ftx-engineering-chief-singh</guid></item><item><title>基于 Solana 的 DeFi 项目 Drift 遭受 2.85 亿美元的攻击</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/solana-based-defi-project-drift-hit-by-285-million-exploit</link><description>据网络安全和数据分析公司称，Drift 是一个基于 Solana 区块链的去中心化金融项目，受到重大漏洞攻击，该协议损失了近 3 亿美元的数字资产。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioQmeBKVq_zE/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 19:25:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/solana-based-defi-project-drift-hit-by-285-million-exploit</guid></item><item><title>比特币支持的市政债券扫清了穆迪评级的障碍</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/bitcoin-backed-municipal-bond-clears-hurdle-with-moody-s-rating</link><description>风险最高的资产类别正在与同类中最安全的金融产品之一融合：比特币支持的市政债券。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i53JkSgE1_dA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 18:58:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/bitcoin-backed-municipal-bond-clears-hurdle-with-moody-s-rating</guid></item><item><title>比特币在连续五个月下跌结束后保持小幅上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/bitcoin-holds-gains-in-asia-after-five-month-losing-streak-ends</link><description>在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普打算在几周内结束对伊朗的战争的推动下，比特币在结束了 3 月份连续五个月的下跌后，周三保持微幅上涨。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ijL7KT0RVqno/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 01:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/bitcoin-holds-gains-in-asia-after-five-month-losing-streak-ends</guid></item><item><title>Zodia Markets 首席执行官艾哈迈德离开渣打银行支持的加密货币公司</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/zodia-markets-ceo-ahmad-departs-stanchart-backed-crypto-firm</link><description>据知情人士透露，渣打银行旗下加密货币交易子公司 Zodia Markets Holdings Ltd. 的首席执行官已离开该公司。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.hAwjimIt1I/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 09:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/zodia-markets-ceo-ahmad-departs-stanchart-backed-crypto-firm</guid></item><item><title>“区块链岛”因加密货币监管而与欧盟对抗</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/malta-fights-back-against-eu-s-crypto-regulation-plans</link><description>欧洲的金融监管之争通常是通过外交手段进行的。这里是一个措辞简洁的声明，那里是一个隐晦的信号。但在拥有黄金签证、大麻合法化和庞大赌博业的马耳他小岛上，参与规则却有所不同。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iM0dsIlGR7XA/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 04:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/malta-fights-back-against-eu-s-crypto-regulation-plans</guid></item><item><title>由于伊朗乐观情绪，比特币结束了连续五个月的下跌</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/bitcoin-btc-rises-with-risk-assets-as-trump-talks-end-of-iran-war</link><description>随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普和伊朗表示愿意结束中东冲突，比特币打破了长达五个月的连续下跌，录得自 9 月份以来的首次月度上涨。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i64i8N6HqTi8/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 05:13:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/bitcoin-btc-rises-with-risk-assets-as-trump-talks-end-of-iran-war</guid></item><item><title>加密货币的周末交易平台被证明是有先见之明的</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-31/crypto-s-weekend-trading-venues-are-proving-to-be-prescient</link><description>打开定价冲突的窗口&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iiSNGfkkJblQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-31/crypto-s-weekend-trading-venues-are-proving-to-be-prescient</guid></item><item><title>Block 的 Dorsey 概述了人工智能驱动的削减中层管理人员的愿景</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/block-s-dorsey-outlines-ai-powered-vision-to-cut-middle-managers</link><description>在 Block Inc. 宣布裁员近一半后几周，杰克·多尔西 (Jack Dorsey) 在重新构想科技公司的运作方式时，将人工智能作为中层管理人员的替代品。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i228Gfmczcvc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 19:05:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/block-s-dorsey-outlines-ai-powered-vision-to-cut-middle-managers</guid></item><item><title>Tether 从汇丰银行聘请黄金交易员几个月后裁员</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/tether-cuts-top-gold-traders-months-after-hiring-them-from-hsbc</link><description>Tether Holdings SA 在从汇丰控股有限公司聘用两名高级贵金属交易员几个月后，裁掉了两名高级贵金属交易员，以创建所谓的“世界上最好的黄金交易大厅”。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3Yp1BMvIAoY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 12:17:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/tether-cuts-top-gold-traders-months-after-hiring-them-from-hsbc</guid></item></channel></rss>